  <num>50-1731.03</num>
  <heading>Prohibition on distracted driving.</heading>
  <text>Distracted driving shall be prohibited. A person found guilty of distracted driving shall be subject to the fines and penalties set forth in <cite path="§50-1731.06|(a)">§ 50-1731.06(a)</cite>.</text>
  <annotations>
